<br>
In retrospect the only class capable of  consistently killing a bard is probably a WIZ becuz we're the only ones with fast enough, and reliable enough nukes.<br>
<br>
Granted &quot;killing&quot; a bard is damn near impossible....in my experiences they are more annoying than anything else...<br>
<br>
They usually just kite with you with annul song.....- wow I sit and click some Jboots and that solves that....like I said annoying - not really a threat...<br>
<br>
So they actually have the gonads to attack you?  Good.....use your fastest casting spells - you will usually get a nice handful of them off before they break epic rune....and once you land that one that hurts they run......if timing is good u can usually get &quot;one more blast&quot; before Selo's takes them away...<br>
<br>
They Selo, they regen, they return......<br>
<br>
BRDs take too long to kill us - especially with Epic + Yonder.....but on the flipside its a timing issue with our ability to kill them (barring Manaburn/a lucky crit).<br>
<br>
A few tactics to try - all have worked....<br>
<br>
Try using that long cast time spell - I seem to be able to channel Ice Comet over 50% of the time.....IC hits a BRD and yeah yer taking that chance of &quot;big damage or no damage&quot; - but with BRDs you HAVE the time to take chances on stuff like that.<br>
<br>
Another tactic is to simply use that 3.0 sec Draught.  Almost a guaranteed hit every time - only problem is not a large chunk of damage taken.....which gives THEM time to just annoy you more <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I think I've died once to a BRD in all my EQ career and it was cuz we were both at 5% life and I thougt it would be kewl to try and win this one out ya know?  Shock of Lightning got interrupted and I died..blah.  <br>
<br>
Anywayz - like I said - BRDs arent a real &quot;threat&quot; per se - they are just annoying becuz to them - almost NO class is a threat becuz of Selo's + Regen + tracking.<br>
<br>
Of course there is the occasional &quot;wild hair&quot; but for the most part this pretty much sums up BRD vs WIZ PvP. <p>"Those that can, do.  Those that cannot, summon pets."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvelaelsoulrender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Velael Soulrender</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>The Likeable SZer</span><br>  Posts: 595<br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/26/02 8:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wanna PvP?  Read and Learn (EDIT 11/29)</span><hr size=1> I'm assuming you haven't fought to many bards with the mana-drain song <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Losing 300m every 15 seconds is vile.<br>
